OL,3,CThames Water boss defends #195K bonus
OL,4,Cdespite company's 'excessive' debt
OL,6,FChris Weston, alongside chairman Sir
OL,7,FAdrian Montague, and chief financial
OL,8,Fofficer Steve Buck, was being quizzed
OL,9,Fon the water company's "hair-raising"
OL,10,Ffinancial situation by the MPs at the
OL,11,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,12,FCommittee this morning.
OL,14,FWhen asked by MPs if it was wise to
OL,15,Faccept such a large bonus so soon into
OL,16,Fthe job at the struggling water
OL,17,Fcompany, Mr Weston said: "I think in
OL,18,Fthe first three months I did make a
OL,19,Fdifference.
OL,26,@yD@ZOU
