OL,3,CThames Water boss defends #195K bonus
OL,4,Cdespite company's 'excessive' debt
OL,6,F"I started to put in place the new
OL,7,Forganisational structure, I started to
OL,8,Fgive people confidence and reassurance
OL,9,Fabout how proud they could be of the
OL,10,Fjob they did and what we were setting
OL,11,Fout to do.
OL,13,F"And that helped stabilise the company
OL,14,Fand I think that was important."
OL,16,F"It is a big ship to turn around. It
OL,17,Fis very difficult."
