OL,3,CThames Water boss defends #195K bonus
OL,4,Cdespite company's 'excessive' debt
OL,6,FWhen asked by MPs about Thames'
OL,7,Ffinances, he admitted on several
OL,8,Foccasions last year Thames Water has
OL,9,Fcome very close to running out of
OL,10,Fmoney entirely.
OL,12,F"There were times in the last year
OL,13,Fthat we had five weeks' liquidity `
OL,14,Fand running a #20 billion corporation
OL,15,Fon five weeks' liquidity, honestly,
OL,16,Fit's hair-raising," Mr Weston said.
OL,18,FHe also acknowledged his firm's levels
OL,19,Fof debt were "excessive," but said
OL,20,F"debt is a very important part of the
OL,21,Fmodel of the water industry".
