OL,3,CThames Water boss defends #195K bonus
OL,4,Cdespite company's 'excessive' debt
OL,6,FDespite the financial issues, the
OL,7,Fbosses said they were prepared for a
OL,8,Fdrought this summer - though it did
OL,9,Fcome "dangerously close" to running
OL,10,Fout of water in the drought summer of
OL,11,F2022 and paying for a #150 million
OL,12,Fdesalination plant that is not working
OL,13,Fyet.
OL,15,FThames Water's chairman Sir Adrian
OL,16,FMontague then apologised for "letting
OL,17,Fcustomers down".
