OL,3,CThames Water boss defends #195K bonus
OL,4,Cdespite company's 'excessive' debt
OL,6,FHe said: "We know that pollutions, we
OL,7,Fknow that spills, we know that supply
OL,8,Finterruptions cause inconvenience and
OL,9,Fsometimes real hardship.
OL,11,F"So I think the right thing to do is
OL,12,Fto start a discussion of the
OL,13,Fturnaround plan by acknowledging that
OL,14,Fwe haven't always served our customers
OL,15,Fas well as we should, and through the
OL,16,Fcommittee apologising to them."
